[CodeReviewHub](https://www.codereviewhub.com) will add these hooks automatically to projects which you enable on www.codereviewhub.com

GitHub Code Reviews made easy
-----------------------------

- Keep track of unaddressed comments.
- Keep track of open issues.
- No more lost file comments due to changing diffs!

Install Notes
-------------

1.  Sign up at https://www.codereviewhub.com with your github account
2.  Add your repository
3.  You're ready!

For more details about CodeReviewHub, go to https://www.codereviewhub.com.
